      </nav>
      <h2 class="work_location bold uppercase">Sites</h2>
      <p class="paragraph">These are sites I designed and built. They display my knowledge of design, usability, and programming.</p>
      <div id="site_block_container">
        <div class="spacer_25"></div>

        <div class="site_block">
          <h3 class="site_title bold"><a href="http://www.google.com" title="O&G Magnolia" class="red">O&G MAGNOLIA</a></h3>
          <div class="spacer_10"></div>
          <p class="paragraph">Insurance/liability & asset management experts.</p>
          <%= link_to image_tag("sites/ogmagnolia_home.png"), image_path("sites/ogmagnolia_home.png"), class: "site_img_link",  title: "O&G Magnolia" %>
          <div class="spacer_25"></div>
          <h4>Target Users:</h4><p class="paragraph">Potential/current investors for company. Those curious about Warren Buffet's and other investing strategies.</p>
          <h4>Site Purpose/Goal:</h4><p class="paragraph">Inform potential/current investors about company and strategy. Convert users/visitors to sign up/subscribe to the newsletter.</p>
          <h4>My Involvement:</h4><p class="paragraph">Redesigned layout/IA/ and implemented design using HTML5/CSS3.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer_50"></div>

        <div class="site_block">
          <h3 class="site_title bold"><a href="http://www.awakewomen.net/" title="AWAKE Women" class="red">AWAKE Women</a></h3>
          <div class="spacer_10"></div>
          <p class="paragraph">Alliance of Women Achieving Knowledge and Excellence</p>
          <%= link_to image_tag("sites/Purple-Space.jpg"), image_path("sites/Purple-Space.jpg"), class: "site_img_link",  title: "AWAKE Women" %>
          <div class="spacer_25"></div>
          <h4>Target Users:</h4><p class="paragraph">Professional women. Non-profit for connecting professional women. Women who are a part of the organization and want to find details of upcoming events. Opportunities to help. Women who want to find out more about the organization and become members.</p>
          <h4>Site Purpose/Goal:</h4><p class="paragraph">Inform users about non-profit. Show upcoming and past events. Get people to contribute organization, funding, events, work. Get people to sign up as members.</p>
          <h4>My Involvement:</h4><p class="paragraph">Redesign already live website. Question users. UI/UX, layout, IA. Implemented through WordPress. Make page communicate goal/purpose more clearly. Fit target audience more appropriately. Organize content into member/non member.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer_50"></div>

        <div class="site_block">
          <h3 class="site_title bold"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/" title="YouTube" class="red">YouTube</a></h3>
          <div class="spacer_10"></div>
          <p class="paragraph">Hosts user-generated videos. Includes network and professional content.</p>
          <%= link_to image_tag("sites/youtube_home.png"), image_path("sites/youtube_home.png"), class: "site_img_link",  title: "YouTube" %>
          <div class="spacer_25"></div>
          <h4>Target Users:</h4><p class="paragraph">People who want to share and view content.</p>
          <h4>Site Purpose/Goal:</h4><p class="paragraph">Allows users to upload, view, and share videos, and make use of Adobe Flash Video and HTML5 technology to display a wide variety of user-generated and corporate media video.</p>
          <h4>My Involvement:</h4><p class="paragraph">Built the whole damn thing.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
